data.description: SE Salem haven boasts an abundance of space & endless possibilities with generously sized bedrooms & flexible rooms that can be transformed into a workout area, home office, or whatever suits your lifestyle! The grand chef's kitchen features a spacious cook island & unique design elements that make it a culinary delight conjoined with the elegant dining room complete with built-in cabinetry. Outbuilding equipped with power, offering the perfect canvas for potential guest quarters or a dream workshop!
